<?php $__env->startSection('postContent'); ?><p><strong>Purpose:</strong></p>
<p>This course teaches drawing skills and design processes. Students will learn new drawing skills, then be asked to apply these skills to a range of stimulating 2D and 3D design tasks. The focus is on learning visual communication skills.</p>
<p><strong>Content:</strong></p>
<p>2D and 3D freehand sketching skills. Instrumental drawing techniques including orthographic projection and pictorial drawing. Application of design processes and use of colour. Students will also have the opportunity to use CAD and 3D printing.</p>
<p><strong>Assessment:</strong></p>
<p>Design assignments and individual drawings.</p><?php $__env->stopSection(); ?>
